    Welcome to The Beast's Domain, a Multi-Player, Interactive, Real-Time, ANSI
adventure game!  The Beast's Domain can handle up to 250 simultaneous players,
and is just as fun for BBS's with only a single line!
    This documentation will help you set-up The Beast's Domain for play on your
system, quickly and easily.



