NOTE: The following limitations have been placed on the DEMO version to
      encourage registration:

      * 10 minutes allowed per player

      * 2 plays per day maximum (not configurable)

      * Cost per minute is always 0 (not configurable)

      * Player position is NOT saved (always starts back at entry point
        when re-entering the game)

